name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save Tab Groups for Tab Session Manager

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Additional extension for saving tab groups in Tab Session Manager

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An extension for Tab Session Manager to support tab groups. 
Please install the Tab Session Manager and enable the "Save Tab Groups" option.
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tab-session-manager/iaiomicjabeggjcfkbimgmglanimpnae
